#v(0.2em)

This example illustrates the visual and layout differences between three modes of Khmer line wrapping.
You can toggle the visual ZWS/SHY indicators on/off using the *Pilcrow button (В¶)* in the toolbar or the *Invisibles* button in the status bar.

